<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>-------<BR>CLASS: Ranger</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>HP: Important when soloing<BR>Mana: Important when soloing<BR>Endurance: only use it when running for my life.<BR>AC: Important when soloing</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>HP Regen: Wish I could get more. Makes for nasty downtime<BR>Mana Regen: Meditate makes for more then siffucient regen with the lower mana pool of a hybrid class.<BR>Endurance Regen: not important</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Strength: Increases melee damage<BR>Stamina: Increases HP, important when soloing<BR>Agility: 2nd most important stat as it increases chance to avoid hits, parry, and riposte.<BR>Dexterity: Most important stat as it increases archery damage and also helps get melee skillups when levelling.<BR>Charisma: Pfft. Buff it only when selling junk loot to NPC vendors.<BR>Intelligence: Pfft.<BR>Wisdom: 3rd most important stat as it increases mana pool</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Resists:&nbsp;Important when raiding<BR></DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Attack: Must have more attack. It increases DPS.<BR>Delay: low delay weapons great for procs and melee skillups<BR>Damage: more damage = more better DPS<BR>Range: Only matters when pulling or bow kiting. </DIV>
<DIV>Haste: Must have more! Increases DPS.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
